{"tid":1383495,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大哥哥大姐姐助養小朋友計劃","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T21:05:38.000Z","uid":258042,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"589a7cabbaf62dcc7690594e7c085d2df9cc659c","tid":1383495,"uid":258042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:53:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日聽到好多關於小朋友努力上進，<br />\n但係礙於經濟上既困難而令到佢地既境況咁慘。<br />\n作為哥哥我都聽到好心酸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而同一時間亦都有好多哥哥姐姐想助養呢一班小朋友，<br />\n所以唔知以下呢個方法得唔得，姑且拋磚引玉</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地可以係每次同呢班小朋友gathering既日子，喺大堂度準備一張張<span style=\"color: violet;\">過左膠既紙條，釘咗窿扣條繩做鎖匙扣，上面寫『我要請細路食飯』</span>，比我地有能力又想助養兒童既人扣係個袋度</span><br />\n<br />\n畀小朋友清楚知道 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">呢個哥哥姐姐想助養我<br />\n我唔駛怕醜</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就好似飯券咁，一個扣代表可以助養一位小朋友一餐，有能力既咪拎多幾個匙扣，助養幾位小朋友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地D哥哥姐姐最撚中意做善事，<br />\n你地班塞豆窿咪再扮怕醜吾畀機會我地包養你<br />\n咁睇唔起我地 講起都火撚滾</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地肚餓都唔肯講<br />\n係撚唔係要我地咁ON9逐個逐個捉你地黎問呀</span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3351a36dd1cc2baa61210ab4c4d3289d2e37b075","tid":1383495,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:55:27.000Z","msg":"唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},{"pid":"4149076af4c293e323121149674aaf34ab78484f","tid":1383495,"uid":5993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個唔會搵你食飯收錢 只要你肯黎拎就得"},{"pid":"18baf42727f9c3c1024ab71c684df839ec771a44","tid":1383495,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:37:00.000Z","msg":"前線有飯開有裝備<br />\n大人有錢出有幫手<br />\n<br />\n[急推］HKTVmall員工助養小朋友計劃正式啟動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大人記得罷工支持呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f8de54ae346f0f8be3d02997d8fc528838d0e9","tid":1383495,"uid":144483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T20:05:00.000Z","msg":"多謝你地呀<br />\n但求下你地多啲買gear買gear買gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實小朋友唔係個個都有嚴重經濟問題<br />\n我地已經唔介意食煙 擋子彈<br />\n又點會介意食小一兩餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心好多謝你地<br />\n但一餐可以平平地自己解決到<br />\ngear就真係好貴 講緊下下幾百起跳。。有啲負擔唔起<br />\n我唔想再見到有手足乜都冇就衝上最前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明白你地真係好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下你地 幫手買gear<br />\n多個眼罩頭盔豬咀 就少個人受傷被捕呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個真係最幫到手<br />\n買完找去現場 睇下邊個小朋友冇裝就塞比佢最岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你<br />\n<br />\n以下係需要既物資 <br />\n請幫手傳開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭盔：攀岩頭盔、電單車頭盔<br />\n<br />\n眼罩：3m GG2891S（唔戴眼鏡）<br />\n3m 2890s<br />\nSellstrom s80225/6<br />\nBolle 40100<br />\nBolle superblast 40926<br />\n<br />\n豬嘴：6200/6300 6500 7500<br />\n濾罐：60926 60921 60923 60925 60928<br />\n<br />\n手臂：冰袖（需配搭保鮮紙）<br />\n濕水棉質護手<br />\n長袖衫<br />\n<br />\n手套：電單車手套<br />\n<br />\n腳：護脛"},{"pid":"ab8e0ab0dbc1e9c4999c83be7c4651513650ceab","tid":1383495,"uid":260887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T20:14:02.000Z","msg":"可能寫「我想請人陪我食飯」好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a0c0af11f20bf3d99352a51bd42e12bbc2d20a","tid":1383495,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T21:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}